[[module CSS]]
.warning-top-box {
  background-color: #e3e3e3;
  border: 2px solid #a1a1a1;
  border-radius: 2px;
  width: 50%;
  margin: 0 auto 2em;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 10px;
}

@media (max-width: 479px) {
  .archived-top-box {
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 0 2em;
  }
}
@media (min-width: 480px) and (max-width: 580px) {
  .archived-top-box {
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 0.5em 2em;
  }
}
[[/module]]

[[div class="warning-top-box"]]

[[size 150%]]**NOTICE:**[[/size]]

This is a 'more by' page used to list works on the SCP Wiki by a certain author. It is intended to be used and included on that author's pages -- as a result, this page may appear to be unfinished or broken.

Please see [/forum/t-14037405/more-by-pages the announcement thread for 'more by' pages] for more information on what a 'more by' page is.

[!--
See the [[[More By Hub]]] for more information.
--]

[[/div]]

